Redux
it is  a predictable state container for javascript apps

predictalbe in the way of state change

state  container mean managing the state

it is not only for react or tightly couple with react. It is a library for react, angular, vue etc.



Three main core concept of redux

1. store
2. reducer
3. action

							|---->Javascript App----------->|
		store(state container)							Action(tell what to do not how to do)
		(hold the state of your application)
							|<-------reducer(tell how to do)<----|
							
							
To combine multiple reducer we can use combineReducers function from redux library or by using a direct way of doing that


							
	
